    <item>
      <title>中国制定规则加强程序化交易审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/china-enacts-rules-to-tighten-scrutiny-of-programmed-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国证券监管机构发布新规则，加强对程序化交易的审查，为对包括 1.6 万亿元人民币（2,220 亿美元）的量化对冲基金行业在内的机构投资者进行更严格的监管铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-16/china-enacts-rules-to-tighten-scrutiny-of-programmed-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 May 2024 04:29:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
